<br>
I'm very VERY glad that people like you run raids.  I know you have to do some experimentation with the rules, and work on getting people to go.  And I know fear can be harder to attract certain folk than Hate is.  It's great that you're trying so hard - I'm sorry my feedback was couched in negative terms.<br>
